{
  "texts": [
    "DL methods received more attention in the publications than ML algorithms due to their sophisticated features that provide amazing results of performance metrics analysis, particularly accuracy in crop disease detection and classification.",
    "Crop disease severity estimation, in particular, contains few articles because it is a new topic of study.",
    "This is ascertained from the few number of articles available.",
    "This necessitates a greater focus on crop disease severity estimation research in future.",
    "This section presents a review of ML-based and DL-based techniques for crop disease classification, detection, and severity estimation."
  ]
}